531
00:35:11,984 --> 00:35:13,277
That family is really shameless!

532
00:35:13,361 --> 00:35:17,448
They want to destroy our family.
They are animals!

533
00:35:22,411 --> 00:35:24,122
At Basil's burial…

534
00:35:26,999 --> 00:35:28,668
I want you to carry this.

535
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:38,970
Sorry for doubting you.

536
00:35:47,353 --> 00:35:50,439
Why did Basil want George killed?

537
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:53,025
Why did he order you to do it?

538
00:35:53,818 --> 00:35:55,153
Why did you agree?

539
00:35:56,487 --> 00:35:59,407
Samantha, answer me!

540
00:35:59,490 --> 00:36:02,285
Why did you agree to do
what Basil wanted?

541
00:36:05,037 --> 00:36:07,748
Because he was able to record a video
of what happened on the cliff.

542
00:36:14,338 --> 00:36:15,423
What video?

543
00:36:15,506 --> 00:36:16,799
What cliff?

544
00:36:27,018 --> 00:36:30,897
Mother, I accidentally
pushed Paco off the cliff.

545
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,565
What?

546
00:36:34,609 --> 00:36:36,652
It was your sister who pushed my boss!

547
00:36:36,736 --> 00:36:37,862
You fool!

548
00:36:37,945 --> 00:36:39,572
Stop it! Francis!

549
00:36:39,655 --> 00:36:41,741
Don't accuse my sister!
You're crazy!

550
00:36:45,453 --> 00:36:47,872
Mother, I didn't mean to.

551
00:36:47,955 --> 00:36:49,790
I didn't mean to.

552
00:36:50,249 --> 00:36:51,709
But in the video,

553
00:36:51,792 --> 00:36:54,420
it looks like I did it intentionally.

554
00:36:54,503 --> 00:37:00,384
That's why Basil was using it
to blackmail me and make me kill George.

555
00:37:00,468 --> 00:37:02,720
I will not leak the video
but on one condition.

556
00:37:02,803 --> 00:37:05,765
I want you to kill my wife.

557
00:37:06,849 --> 00:37:09,227
But Mother, I didn't do it.

558
00:37:09,310 --> 00:37:10,561
I couldn't.

559
00:37:10,645 --> 00:37:12,688
I couldn't kill George.

560
00:37:12,772 --> 00:37:13,856
I couldn't do it.

561
00:37:27,703 --> 00:37:28,788
That's why…

562
00:37:29,372 --> 00:37:31,540
you poisoned Basil?

563
00:37:31,624 --> 00:37:32,959
Mother, no!

564
00:37:33,042 --> 00:37:35,544
It wasn't me who killed Basil.

565
00:37:35,628 --> 00:37:38,965
I don't know… I don't know who did it.

566
00:37:39,048 --> 00:37:40,758
I don't know who, but…

567
00:37:41,133 --> 00:37:47,265
but I think it was Francis' morphine
that was used to kill Basil.

568
00:38:03,447 --> 00:38:06,909
Did you steal Francis' morphine?

569
00:38:06,993 --> 00:38:10,162
You involved your brother in this mess
you got yourself into?!

570
00:38:10,746 --> 00:38:12,999
You put your brother in danger!

571
00:38:13,082 --> 00:38:15,710
You're the reason he's in jail!

572
00:38:17,003 --> 00:38:19,171
You! It's your fault!

573
00:38:21,090 --> 00:38:24,885
Mother, forgive me.

574
00:38:26,595 --> 00:38:29,932
Forgive me, please.

575
00:38:32,351 --> 00:38:34,020
I will forgive you

576
00:38:35,062 --> 00:38:38,190
when you get your brother out of jail.

577
00:40:02,650 --> 00:40:04,068
What happened?

578
00:40:04,151 --> 00:40:06,779
Ma'am, I'm sorry but it seems
the car broke down.

579
00:40:06,862 --> 00:40:09,365
So how are we going to bring
the casket inside?

580
00:40:09,448 --> 00:40:10,616
We will carry it.

581
00:40:13,369 --> 00:40:14,537
Everyone,

582
00:40:15,413 --> 00:40:16,789
carry the casket.

583
00:40:41,313 --> 00:40:42,356
Let me.

584
00:40:44,066 --> 00:40:45,234
Inigo?

585
00:41:16,390 --> 00:41:17,683
Francis…

586
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:20,811
Francis.

587
00:41:23,772 --> 00:41:25,149
Sam…

588
00:41:25,816 --> 00:41:27,151
Francis…

589
00:41:29,528 --> 00:41:32,031
Sam, it's difficult here.

590
00:41:35,075 --> 00:41:37,286
I'm scared of the inmates
I'm in with, Sam.

591
00:41:37,369 --> 00:41:38,579
I can't sleep.

592
00:42:43,936 --> 00:42:47,273
Who poisoned Basil?
Why am I being accused?

593
00:42:49,191 --> 00:42:50,943
Why have I been dragged into this?

594
00:43:54,757 --> 00:43:55,924
Inigo…

595
00:43:56,717 --> 00:43:58,135
I didn't know you were here.

596
00:44:00,179 --> 00:44:01,430
When did you arrive?

597
00:44:03,849 --> 00:44:05,934
A couple of days ago.

598
00:44:07,186 --> 00:44:08,312
God.

599
00:44:10,272 --> 00:44:12,066
And this is what you see.

600
00:44:19,406 --> 00:44:20,407
Wait.

601
00:44:21,200 --> 00:44:22,910
Excuse me. George?

602
00:44:22,993 --> 00:44:24,578
I need you to meet someone.

603
00:44:32,127 --> 00:44:34,380
This is Attorney Inigo Morales.

604
00:44:36,006 --> 00:44:37,716
He's Basil's best friend.

605
00:44:45,307 --> 00:44:47,976
Please help me, Sam.

606
00:44:49,895 --> 00:44:52,189
- Yes, Francis.
- Please help me.

607
00:44:53,065 --> 00:44:56,360
I will do everything I can
to get you out of here,

608
00:44:56,860 --> 00:44:58,737
I promise you that.

609
00:45:12,835 --> 00:45:16,463
George, Basil's wife.

610
00:45:17,714 --> 00:45:19,091
Nice to meet you, Attorney.

611
00:45:20,050 --> 00:45:22,636
Why did Basil never tell me about you?

612
00:45:29,852 --> 00:45:32,271
NEXT EPISODE

613
00:45:32,354 --> 00:45:34,690
Nor do parents with dead children.

614
00:45:34,773 --> 00:45:36,316
You still have Sofia.

615
00:45:36,400 --> 00:45:40,195
As for me, I'm looking forward
to Paco's child.

616
00:45:40,279 --> 00:45:41,738
It's unfair!

617
00:45:41,822 --> 00:45:44,324
Basil didn't even leave me
with a grandchild.

618
00:45:44,408 --> 00:45:46,410
We have an unwanted guest, Mother.

619
00:45:46,827 --> 00:45:49,538
- Beverly?
- Basil and I had an affair.

620
00:45:49,621 --> 00:45:53,208
So the baby you're carrying
belongs to Basil?

621
00:45:53,292 --> 00:45:54,585
You're unbelievable!

622
00:45:54,668 --> 00:45:56,128
At least I'm not a murderer.

623
00:45:56,211 --> 00:45:58,255
<i>It was you who sent me this, right?</i>

624
00:45:58,338 --> 00:45:59,173
<i>You want me dead.</i>

625
00:45:59,256 --> 00:46:01,049
You wanted Basil all to yourself

626
00:46:01,133 --> 00:46:03,302
and for him to take responsibility
for your baby.

627
00:46:03,385 --> 00:46:04,595
<i>Uncle Galvan…</i>

628
00:46:04,678 --> 00:46:06,597
<i>If you're here to plead</i>
<i>about your brother,</i>

629
00:46:06,680 --> 00:46:07,973
you're wasting your time.

630
00:46:08,056 --> 00:46:09,516
He killed my son!

631
00:46:09,600 --> 00:46:11,393
Oh my God, you're bleeding!

632
00:46:11,477 --> 00:46:13,562
Oh no! My grandchild!
